# Profit Peak Integration for Magento 2

[![Magento Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Magento-2.4.6-brightgreen)](https://magento.com/)

Profit Peak Integration is a powerful Magento 2 extension that enables seamless connectivity between your Magento 2 store and Profit Peak's advanced analytics and optimization platform. This extension allows you to effortlessly track sales, customer journeys, and in-depth product performance, empowering you with insights to grow your eCommerce business.

---

## Features

- **Real-Time Analytics:** Track page views, add-to-cart events, and checkout processes in real time.
- **Customer Journey Tracking:** Map customer journeys from page views to completed purchases.
- **Enhanced Product Insights:** Access performance data for products, including sales trends, average order value, and profit margins.
- **Automated Cost Allocation:** Integrate warehouse, shipping, and merchant fees into product-level cost analysis.
- **Flexible Data Sync:** Automatically push data from your Magento 2 store to Profit Peak for seamless reporting and analysis.

## Usage

Once configured, the Profit Peak Integration extension will start syncing data automatically. You can monitor and analyze your storeâ€™s data within the Profit Peak dashboard.

- **Real-Time Monitoring:** Access real-time insights on customer activity and product performance.
- **Order Analytics:** Get a detailed view of sales performance and order trends.
- **Profitability Insights:** Understand your profits at a granular level with integrated cost tracking.

